item.title: School Acceptance!
item.description: Event date: Friday, 01 Nov 2019 Writing date: Friday, 01 Nov 2019 It finally arrived! The phone call acceptance I’ve been longing for! I admit, the past 24 hours leading to that phone call was anxiety-inducing. Would I get the call at all? A rejection email perhaps? I even told myself I would be happy if I would be put on hold; anything but a rejection! I noticed a missed call from a private number.
